1
00:00:52,719 --> 00:00:53,880
Walking all the way here,

2
00:00:54,159 --> 00:00:55,119
in this place,

3
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:57,359
the walls are completely covered

4
00:00:57,600 --> 00:01:00,359
in black scorch marks from fire blasts.

5
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:02,600
Nowhere else has them, right?

6
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,280
Nope.

7
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,319
So why only here?

8
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:04,640
No idea.

9
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,879
Chiyan Jizhou is so vast.

10
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:07,319
Why is this the only cave

11
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:08,840
with fire blast marks?

12
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:12,200
Well, lizards only seek warm,

13
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:15,319
damp, hidden spots when laying eggs.

14
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,400
Exactly.

15
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:18,560
So that means,

16
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:20,480
above is the mushroom cave,

17
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:22,079
connected to the cave below.

18
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:23,239
It's very damp here.

19
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,000
Why does the lizard keep

20
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,159
spraying fire at this place?

21
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:27,640
To maintain the temperature.

22
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,560
Which means what?

23
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,719
It means its young

24
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:32,079
are right inside this cave.

25
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:33,680
Throw a stone out there.

26
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:36,000
If it spits fire without hesitation,

27
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,879
that means there are no eggs there.

28
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:40,000
If it doesn't spit fire,

29
00:01:42,159 --> 00:01:43,640
it's to avoid burning its own young.

30
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,280
Right.

31
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:47,280
One blast, and they become marbled eggs.

32
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,560
That side won't work.

33
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,639
Neither side works?

34
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:13,960
Let me try this side.

35
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:18,240
Godfather, be careful.

36
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:28,400
Here goes.

37
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,479
It's right here.

38
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,400
Oh my god.

39
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:57,319
If it dares spit fire at me,

40
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:59,919
its babies will become kebabs.

41
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,280
Hurry, let's go.

42
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:01,879
Go!

43
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:03,319
Go!

44
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,560
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

45
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,199
This way, this way!

46
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,479
An Xiang!

47
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,719
Hurry, help him up!

48
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:52,919
Hurry!

49
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,360
Chen Youxi!

50
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:10,560
Shu Tong!

51
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,399
Shu Tong!

52
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:37,240
Advisor He!

53
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,319
Chen Youxi!

54
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,360
Chen Youxi!

55
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,360
Chen Youxi!

56
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:28,000
This place should be safe, right?

57
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:35,360
It's fine, it didn't follow us.

58
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:38,240
An Xiang, you didn't get hurt, did you?

59
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,319
Uncle Min,

60
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,480
you're getting on in years.

61
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,399
Don't you have a heart?

62
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,240
Master Lu.

63
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,000
Master Lu, my foot!

64
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,680
What you're doing is plain murder.

65
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,439
Brother Lu.

66
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:50,560
Come here.

67
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:53,399
Brother Lu, An Xiang.

68
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:55,120
Going now won't save him.

69
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,560
Let go! I'm going!

70
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,399
Let go!

71
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,120
Don't move.

72
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:00,319
You see this, right?

73
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,560
Touch him one more time,

74
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,759
and I'll smash it to pieces.

75
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,759
Save my Godfather!

76
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:07,959
Back then,

77
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,480
I took you out of the orphanage,

78
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,519
and let you grow up carefree.

79
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:19,560
I've

80
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,160
already done enough.

81
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:29,360
Monster, monster, monster!

82
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:35,199
Monster, monster, monster!

83
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,120
No one will play with you, you're a monster!

84
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,519
Monster, monster!

85
00:07:52,079 --> 00:07:53,399
Heterochromia

86
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:56,279
can be either congenital or acquired.

87
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:57,920
Congenital means it's hereditary.

88
00:07:58,279 --> 00:07:59,879
For example, if the parents' eyes

89
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:00,920
have different colors,

90
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,519
then their offspring

91
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,839
might have

92
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:05,319
one blue eye

93
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,639
and one gray eye.

94
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,199
As for the acquired cases,

95
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:11,480
it could be caused by Horner's syndrome

96
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,439
or Iridocyclitis,

97
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:15,040
causing the iris tissue

98
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:17,160
to suffer damage and atrophy.

99
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:21,160
What about the scar on her body?

100
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:23,079
It's a form of capillary hyperplasia.

101
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,079
Compared to her eye color,

102
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:27,360
the consequences of this hyperplasia

103
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:30,399
could cause her heart to fail anytime

104
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:31,920
from an insufficient blood supply.

105
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,240
Take a look. How is it?

106
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,480
I have to say, this tattoo artist

107
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,799
is really skilled.

108
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,240
It looks incredibly real.

109
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,399
Remember,

110
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:53,399
you must casually

111
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,759
let Fatty notice this scar.

112
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:57,799
Understood.

113
00:08:58,559 --> 00:08:59,240
Godfather.

114
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,399
You may leave now.

115
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,039
Yes.

116
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:06,360
An Xiang, come sit down.

117
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:13,399
Sit.

118
00:09:15,039 --> 00:09:16,039
Auntie He said

119
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,559
I can come along on this trip.

120
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:19,519
That's right.

121
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:21,679
Godfather,

122
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,799
about that thing on your back...

123
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:30,360
Since you've already seen it,

124
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,080
I won't hide it from you.

125
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:34,000
I'm doing this

126
00:09:34,399 --> 00:09:36,559
to dispel their suspicions.

127
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,679
When the time comes,

128
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:40,639
I'll divert their attention.

129
00:09:40,919 --> 00:09:42,440
You must take the opportunity

130
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:45,159
to get your hands on the Lingxiao Pearl.

131
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:51,519
Godfather, don't worry.

132
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:53,159
I'll definitely get it for you.

133
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:56,200
Not for me.

134
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,240
It's for you.

135
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:01,200
Only by getting the Lingxiao Pearl

136
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,960
and grasping its secret

137
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,399
can I save you.

138
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,840
I hope you

139
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:13,399
can live on happily and joyfully.

140
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:20,639
Godfather,

141
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:27,120
after all these years,

142
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,200
I've always wanted to ask you something.

143
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:32,600
Go ahead.

144
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,240
Out of so many kids at the orphanage,

145
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,480
why did you choose me?

146
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,000
Why?

147
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,399
Because

148
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,039
you are

149
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:54,279
a descendant of the Mengnagu people.

150
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,679
Yeah, this is just terrible.

151
00:11:23,679 --> 00:11:24,320
Look at that.

152
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,240
How did this happen?

153
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:28,559
This... this...

154
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,159
Is this person okay?

155
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,240
Is he dead?

156
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:34,080
Look how serious it is. Yeah.

157
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,679
Things don't look good.

158
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,639
It was you.

159
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:07,200
You caused my parents' crash, didn't you?

160
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:20,120
Because they wouldn't cooperate.

161
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:22,639
I had no choice.

162
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:29,919
But I really didn't expect

163
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,919
that you, a descendant of the Mengnagu people,

164
00:12:35,039 --> 00:12:36,879
wouldn't help me at all.

165
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,360
Murderer!

166
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,360
An Xiang! An Xiang!

167
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:32,000
An Xiang, are you okay?

168
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,000
It's okay, it's okay. You're awake now.

169
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:41,840
Godfather, he...

170
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:46,200
An Xiang, are you okay?
